For trends use lineplot

For comparison i.e., correlation use barplot,scatterplot,scatterplot with hue,heatmap......Note that barplot uses two variables ....also use
regplot,lmplot

For plotting distributions distplot withe kde=False or True,kdeplot,jointplot
